{"id":1919,"date":"2020-08-24T11:31:45","date_gmt":"2020-08-24T04:31:45","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/?page_id=1919"},"modified":"2020-09-16T15:51:21","modified_gmt":"2020-09-16T08:51:21","slug":"memoirs-of-the-caravelle-vi","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/memoirs-of-the-caravelle-vi\/","title":{"rendered":"H\u1ed3i \u1ee9c v\u1ec1 Caravelle"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-47f6251q fg-image  img-responsive full-width fg-text-dark\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Memoir-of-Caravelle-VN.jpg 1992w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/7a36aedcd220483b0fcab3519d0657dd_Memoir-of-Caravelle-VN-320-c-100.jpg 320w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/7a36aedcd220483b0fcab3519d0657dd_Memoir-of-Caravelle-VN-768-c-100.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/7a36aedcd220483b0fcab3519d0657dd_Memoir-of-Caravelle-VN-992-c-100.jpg 992w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/7a36aedcd220483b0fcab3519d0657dd_Memoir-of-Caravelle-VN-1200-c-100.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1992px) 100vw, 1992px\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Memoir-of-Caravelle-VN.jpg\" alt=\"Memoir-of-Caravelle-VN\"><style><\/style><script type=\"text\/javascript\"><\/script><section class=\"ffb-id-48i42sam fg-section fg-text-dark\" id=\"intro\"><div class=\"fg-container container fg-container-large fg-container-lvl--1 \"><div class=\"fg-row row    \" ><div class=\"ffb-id-48i42san fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-12 fg-text-dark\"><h1 class=\"ffb-id-48i42saq fg-heading text-center    fg-text-dark\">H\u1ed2I \u1ee8C V\u1ec0 CARAVELLE<\/h1><div class=\"ffb-id-48i42sar fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\">Hi\u1ebfm kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n n&agrave;o c&oacute; c&aacute;i t&ecirc;n kh\u01a1i g\u1ee3i h&igrave;nh \u1ea3nh l&atilde;ng m\u1ea1n, d\u1ec5 m\u1ebfn v&agrave; d\u1ec5 h&igrave;nh dung nh\u01b0 Caravelle &ndash; C&aacute;nh bu\u1ed3m. Thanh &acirc;m ng\u1ecdt ng&agrave;o c\u1ee7a t\u1eeb n&agrave;y g\u1ee3i ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb chi\u1ebfc thuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Jamaica, hay nh\u01b0 c&aacute;ch ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph&aacute;p g\u1ecdi ch&uacute;ng l&agrave; &laquo;caravelle&raquo;, nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc thuy\u1ec1n bu\u1ed3m h\u1ea1ng nh\u1eb9, ch\u1ea1y nhanh t\u1eeb th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 15, rong ru\u1ed5i tr&ecirc;n h\u1ea3i tr&igrave;nh kh&aacute;m ph&aacute; th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 t&igrave;m ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i giao th\u01b0\u01a1ng, nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ebfn th&aacute;m hi\u1ec3m v&agrave; ch&acirc;n tr\u1eddi m\u1edbi.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\">V&agrave; c&oacute; l\u1ebd kh&ocirc;ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1eabu nhi&ecirc;n m&agrave; h&atilde;ng h&agrave;ng kh&ocirc;ng Air France, c&ocirc;ng ty n\u1eafm c\u1ed5 ph\u1ea7n trong to&agrave; kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n ban \u0111\u1ea7u, \u0111\u1eb7t v\u0103n ph&ograve;ng t\u1ea1i \u0111&acirc;y ngay khi khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111&atilde; cho v\u1eadn h&agrave;nh lo\u1ea1i m&aacute;y bay ph\u1ea3n l\u1ef1c m\u1edbi l\u1ea1 c&oacute; c&ugrave;ng t&ecirc;n g\u1ecdi.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\">Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n Caravelle \u0111&atilde; ch&iacute;nh th\u1ee9c m\u1edf c\u1eeda v&agrave;o \u0111&ecirc;m v\u1ecdng Gi&aacute;ng Sinh n\u0103m 1959, chi&ecirc;u \u0111&atilde;i c&ocirc;ng ch&uacute;ng b\u1eb1ng b\u1eefa ti\u1ec7c canap&eacute; tr&ecirc;n nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc khay b\u1eb1ng b\u1ea1c l\u1ea5p l&aacute;nh, th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c c&ugrave;ng r\u01b0\u1ee3u S&acirc;m panh c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n trong b\u1ea7u kh&ocirc;ng kh&iacute; l\u1ec5 h\u1ed9i t\u01b0\u01a1i vui v&agrave; \u1ea5m &aacute;p. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, to&agrave; nh&agrave; \u0111&atilde; m\u1edf c\u1eeda tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111&oacute; b\u1ea3y th&aacute;ng, khi m\u1ed9t t\u1edd b&aacute;o \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111&atilde; n\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u01b0a tin v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n l&aacute;t \u0111&aacute; hoa c\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u t\u1eeb &Yacute; v&agrave; \u0111\u01b0a k&iacute;nh ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ea1n v&agrave;o s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. C&ograve;n c&oacute; m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b&agrave;i vi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a ph&oacute;ng vi&ecirc;n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t &laquo;h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ho&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng kh&iacute; v&agrave; m&aacute;y ph&aacute;t \u0111i\u1ec7n d\u1ef1 ph&ograve;ng hi\u1ec7u Berliet hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t&raquo; th\u1eddi \u0111&oacute;.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\">Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, t&aacute;c ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a hai ki\u1ebfn tr&uacute;c s\u01b0, m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph&aacute;p v&agrave; m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi Vi\u1ec7t, v&agrave; h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u01a1 s\u1edf v\u1eadt ch\u1ea5t t&acirc;n ti\u1ebfn n&agrave;y s\u1edbm tr\u1edf th&agrave;nh tr\u1ee5 s\u1edf c\u1ee7a c&aacute;c To&agrave; \u0111\u1ea1i s\u1ee9, v\u0103n ph&ograve;ng c\u1ee7a c&aacute;c h&atilde;ng th&ocirc;ng t\u1ea5n v&agrave; doanh nghi\u1ec7p. Trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m 1960, Caravelle l&agrave; \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ea1i s\u1ee9 qu&aacute;n &Uacute;c, \u0110\u1ea1i s\u1ee9 qu&aacute;n New Zealand, v\u0103n ph&ograve;ng&nbsp; th\u01b0\u1eddng tr&uacute; t\u1ea1i S&agrave;i G&ograve;n c\u1ee7a c&aacute;c h&atilde;ng tin t\u1ee9c nh\u01b0 NBC, ABC v&agrave; CBS.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\">Ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian, bao tr&ugrave;m kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n Caravelle l&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng kh&iacute; y\u1ebfn ti\u1ec7c t\u01b0\u01a1i vui. Qu&aacute;n bar tr&ecirc;n s&acirc;n th\u01b0\u1ee3ng l&agrave; n\u01a1i v\u1eeba t&aacute;c nghi\u1ec7p v&agrave; giao l\u01b0u c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th&ocirc;ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf. T\u1eeb t\u1ea7ng m\u01b0\u1eddi, v\u1edbi ly bia l\u1ea1nh trong tay, v&agrave;o nh\u1eefng ng&agrave;y cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n kh&eacute;p l\u1ea1i, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n ng\u1ed3i ngay t\u1ea1i gh\u1ebf bar, c&aacute;c nh&agrave; b&aacute;o c&oacute; th\u1ec3 nh&igrave;n th\u1ea5y ti\u1ec1n tuy\u1ebfn, v&agrave; m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 &iacute;t c&ograve;n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd c&oacute; th\u1ec3 vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 c&aacute;c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng c\u1ea7n r\u1eddi ch\u1ed7 ng\u1ed3i y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch c\u1ee7a m&igrave;nh.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\">Tr\u1ea3i qua l\u1ecbch s\u1eed nhi\u1ec1u thay \u0111\u1ed5i v&agrave; m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n mang c&oacute; t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn, c&oacute; th\u1ec3 n&oacute;i r\u1eb1ng ngo&agrave;i qu\u1ea7y bar s&acirc;n th\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng, th&igrave; Ph&ograve;ng 514 c&oacute; l\u1ebd l&agrave; ch\u1ee9ng nh&acirc;n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho nh\u1eefng g&igrave; \u0111&atilde; di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf Caravelle v&agrave; xung quanh th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1 th\u1eddi b\u1ea5y gi\u1edd. Sau ng&agrave;y S&agrave;i G&ograve;n gi\u1ea3i ph&oacute;ng 1975, ch&iacute;nh ph\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n, v\u1eadn h&agrave;nh v&agrave; \u0111\u1ed5i t&ecirc;n th&agrave;nh Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n \u0110\u1ed9c L\u1eadp (Independence). Cho \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 1998, Caravelle &ndash; c&aacute;i t&ecirc;n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb th\u1ebf kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n cao c\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t trong th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1 \u0111&atilde; m\u1edf c\u1eeda tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, n\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t ch&agrave;o \u0111&oacute;n du kh&aacute;ch nh\u01b0 thu\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\">To&agrave; nh&agrave; ban \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi 10 t\u1ea7ng nay \u0111&atilde; li\u1ec1n k\u1ec1 v\u1edbi t&ograve;a th&aacute;p m\u1edbi 24 t\u1ea7ng t\u1ea1o n&ecirc;n c\u1ea5u tr&uacute;c t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 m\u1edbi. Ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0, n\u1ebfu kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; t\u1ea7m nh&igrave;n xa, r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ph&aacute; c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh c\u0169 v&agrave; x&acirc;y m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n. V\u1edbi ch&uacute;ng ta, th\u1eadt kh&ocirc;ng th\u1ec3 n&agrave;o h&igrave;nh dung nh\u1eefng g&oacute;c ban c&ocirc;ng u\u1ed1n l\u01b0\u1ee3n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt g\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda th\u1ebf k\u1ef7, l&agrave; m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n kh&ocirc;ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a qu\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1 c&oacute; th\u1ec3 bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t. Quang c\u1ea3nh t\u1eeb t\u1ea7ng th\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c&aacute;c ph&oacute;ng vi&ecirc;n n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo&agrave;i y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch gi\u1edd \u0111&acirc;y \u0111&atilde; tr\u1edf th&agrave;nh kh&ocirc;ng gian c\u1ee7a Saigon Saigon Bar, v\u1edbi n&eacute;t \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng nguy&ecirc;n thu\u1ef7 v\u1ed1n c&oacute; t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1959.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\">N\u1ebfu nh&igrave;n sang Nh&agrave; H&aacute;t Th&agrave;nh Ph\u1ed1 v&agrave; Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n Continental, d\u1ecdc theo \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ed3ng Kh\u1edfi, b\u1ea1n v\u1eabn c&oacute; th\u1ec3 nh&igrave;n th\u1ea5y ng\u1ecdn th&aacute;p \u0111&ocirc;i c\u1ee7a Nh&agrave; th\u1edd \u0110\u1ee9c B&agrave;. D\u1ecdc theo con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n&agrave;y, v\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l&agrave; \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Catinat v&agrave;o n\u0103m 1975, m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc xe t\u0103ng c\u1ee7a qu&acirc;n \u0111\u1ed9i Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111&atilde; ti\u1ebfn v&agrave;o Place Garnier, nay l&agrave; C&ocirc;ng Tr\u01b0\u1eddng Lam S\u01a1n. K&eacute;o th&aacute;p ph&aacute;o v&agrave; nh\u1eafm v&agrave;o m\u1eb7t ti\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n. T\u1ea1i sao l&uacute;c \u0111&oacute; xe t\u0103ng kh&ocirc;ng khai ho\u1ea3, lu&ocirc;n l&agrave; s\u1ef1 ph\u1ecfng \u0111o&aacute;n c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Tuy v\u1eady, nh\u1eefng ai \u0111ang d\u1ea1o b\u01b0\u1edbc tr&ecirc;n s&acirc;n th\u01b0\u1ee3ng, v\u1edbi \u0111&ocirc;i m\u1eaft bi\u1ebft \u01a1n d&agrave;nh cho g&oacute;c di s\u1ea3n n&agrave;y c\u1ee7a th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1, ph\u1ea3i ch\u0103ng \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n n&acirc;ng m\u1ed9t ho\u1eb7c hai ly cho b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai \u0111&atilde; ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ec1u th&aacute;ng T\u01b0 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111&oacute;.<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section><style>.ffb-id-48i42sam{ padding-top: 50px;padding-right: 50px;padding-bottom: 50px;padding-left: 50px;}.ffb-id-48i42sar ,.ffb-id-48i42sar:before,.ffb-id-48i42sar:after,.ffb-id-48i42sar *,.ffb-id-48i42sar *:before,.ffb-id-48i42sar *:after{ color: #490042 !important;}.ffb-id-48i42sar{ font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;}.ffb-id-48i42sar:before,.ffb-id-48i42sar:after,.ffb-id-48i42sar:hover,.ffb-id-48i42sar:focus,.ffb-id-48i42sar *,.ffb-id-48i42sar *:before,.ffb-id-48i42sar *:after,.ffb-id-48i42sar *:hover,.ffb-id-48i42sar *:focus{ font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;}.ffb-id-48i42sar{ font-size: 13px !important;}.ffb-id-48i42sar ,.ffb-id-48i42sar:before,.ffb-id-48i42sar:after,.ffb-id-48i42sar:hover,.ffb-id-48i42sar:focus,.ffb-id-48i42sar *,.ffb-id-48i42sar *:before,.ffb-id-48i42sar *:after,.ffb-id-48i42sar *:hover,.ffb-id-48i42sar *:focus{ font-size: 13px !important;}.ffb-id-48i42saq ,.ffb-id-48i42saq:before,.ffb-id-48i42saq:after,.ffb-id-48i42saq *,.ffb-id-48i42saq *:before,.ffb-id-48i42saq *:after{ color: #490042 !important;}.ffb-id-48i42saq{ font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;}.ffb-id-48i42saq:before,.ffb-id-48i42saq:after,.ffb-id-48i42saq:hover,.ffb-id-48i42saq:focus,.ffb-id-48i42saq *,.ffb-id-48i42saq *:before,.ffb-id-48i42saq *:after,.ffb-id-48i42saq *:hover,.ffb-id-48i42saq *:focus{ font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;}<\/style><script type=\"text\/javascript\"><\/script><div class=\"ffb-id-48i436gr fg-row row fg-row-no-gutter    fg-el-has-bg fg-text-dark\" id=\"row 1\"><span class=\"fg-bg\"><span data-fg-bg=\"{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;color&quot;,&quot;opacity&quot;:1,&quot;color&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\" class=\"fg-bg-layer fg-bg-type-color \" style=\"opacity: 1; background-color: ;\"><\/span><\/span><div class=\"ffb-id-48i436gs fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-6 fg-text-dark\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-48i436h0 fg-image  img-responsive full-width fg-text-dark\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Caravelle-Terrace-Draft-Photo.jpg\" alt=\"Caravelle-Terrace-Draft-Photo\"><h2 class=\"ffb-id-48i436h1 fg-heading text-center    fg-text-dark\">CARAVELLE NG\u00c0Y \u1ea4Y<\/h2><div class=\"ffb-id-48i436h2 fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p>Hi\u1ebfm kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n n&agrave;o c&oacute; c&aacute;i t&ecirc;n kh\u01a1i g\u1ee3i h&igrave;nh \u1ea3nh l&atilde;ng m\u1ea1n, d\u1ec5 m\u1ebfn v&agrave; d\u1ec5 h&igrave;nh dung nh\u01b0 The Caravelle &ndash; C&aacute;nh bu\u1ed3m. Thanh &acirc;m ng\u1ecdt ng&agrave;o c\u1ee7a t\u1eeb n&agrave;y g\u1ee3i ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb chi\u1ebfc thuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Jamaica, hay nh\u01b0 c&aacute;ch ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph&aacute;p g\u1ecdi ch&uacute;ng l&agrave; &ldquo;caravelle&rdquo;, nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc thuy\u1ec1n bu\u1ed3m h\u1ea1ng nh\u1eb9, ch\u1ea1y nhanh t\u1eeb th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 15, rong ru\u1ed5i tr&ecirc;n h\u1ea3i tr&igrave;nh kh&aacute;m ph&aacute; th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 t&igrave;m ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i giao th\u01b0\u01a1ng, nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ebfn th&aacute;m hi\u1ec3m, v&agrave; ch&acirc;n tr\u1eddi m\u1edbi.<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-48i436h3 fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-6 fg-el-has-bg fg-text-dark\"><span class=\"fg-bg\"><span data-fg-bg=\"{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;color&quot;,&quot;opacity&quot;:1,&quot;color&quot;:&quot;#ffffff&quot;}\" class=\"fg-bg-layer fg-bg-type-color \" style=\"opacity: 1; background-color: #ffffff;\"><\/span><\/span><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-48i436h7 fg-image  img-responsive full-width fg-text-dark\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/News-680x472-Caravelle-now.jpg\" alt=\"News-680x472-Caravelle-now\"><h2 class=\"ffb-id-48i436h8 fg-heading text-center    fg-text-dark\">CARAVELLE B\u00c2Y GI\u1edc<\/h2><div class=\"ffb-id-48i436h9 fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p>N\u0103m 1998, l&agrave; th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 chuy\u1ec3n m&igrave;nh t\u1eeb n&eacute;t l\u1ed9ng l\u1eaby c\u1ee7a ki\u1ebfn tr&uacute;c Ph&aacute;p nguy&ecirc;n thu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ebfn d&aacute;ng v\u1ebb sang tr\u1ecdng, hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Caravelle. V\u1edbi 3 n\u0103m li&ecirc;n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ea1t gi\u1ea3i Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n H&agrave;ng \u0111\u1ea7u T\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, Caravelle Saigon l&agrave; kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n 5 sao h&agrave;ng \u0111\u1ea7u trong th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><\/div><style>.ffb-id-48i42sam{ \npadding-top: 50px;\npadding-right: 50px;\npadding-bottom: 50px;\npadding-left: 50px;\n\n}\n.ffb-id-48i42sar ,\n.ffb-id-48i42sar:before,\n.ffb-id-48i42sar:after,\n.ffb-id-48i42sar *,\n.ffb-id-48i42sar *:before,\n.ffb-id-48i42sar *:after{ \ncolor: #490042 !important;\n}\n.ffb-id-48i42sar{ \nfont-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;\n}\n.ffb-id-48i42sar:before,\n.ffb-id-48i42sar:after,\n.ffb-id-48i42sar:hover,\n.ffb-id-48i42sar:focus,\n.ffb-id-48i42sar *,\n.ffb-id-48i42sar *:before,\n.ffb-id-48i42sar *:after,\n.ffb-id-48i42sar *:hover,\n.ffb-id-48i42sar *:focus{ \nfont-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;\n}\n.ffb-id-48i42sar{ \nfont-size: 13px !important;\n}\n.ffb-id-48i42sar ,\n.ffb-id-48i42sar:before,\n.ffb-id-48i42sar:after,\n.ffb-id-48i42sar:hover,\n.ffb-id-48i42sar:focus,\n.ffb-id-48i42sar *,